text: Tanza Varela (born Constanza Andrea Varela de la Barra on 15 April 1991 in Temuco) is a Chilean actress and model. == Television works == === Telenovelas === * 2009: Corazón Rebelde (Canal 13) as Victoria "Vico" López === Series === * 2010: Infieles (Chilevisión) on 2 episodes === Programs === * 2010: Sin Dios ni Late (Zona Latina) as Herself * 2010: Mira quién habla (Mega) as Commentator * 2010: SQP (Chilevisión) as Herself * 2010: Primer plano (Chilevisión) as Herself * 2010: Teatro en Chilevisión (Chilevisión) as María Javiera (episode: La reina de las divas) * 2010: En portada (UCV TV) as Reporter * 2011: Año 0 (Canal 13) as Herself (Participant) * 2011: Morandé con compañía (Mega) as Herself (episode of the day 27 May 2011) * 2011: El experimento (TVN) as Jury * 2012: Mundos opuestos (Canal 13) as Herself * 2012: Amazonas (Chilevisión) as Herself (Participant) * 2012: Primer plano (Chilevisión) as Herself * 2012: Intrusos (La Red) as Commentator * 2013: Mundos opuestos 2 (Canal 13) as Herself * 2013: Ruleta Rusa (Canal 13) as Herself (Participant) == Other websites == * Category:1991 births Category:Chilean models Category:Chilean television actors Category:Living people Category:People from Araucanía Region
